sequenceDiagram
  actor Human
  participant Matrix as Matrix Homeserver
  participant Gateway as Matrix AppService Gateway
  participant API as Runtime API
  participant Store as Task Store
  participant Router as Capability Router
  participant Policy as Policy Engine
  participant WCM as Work Cell Manager
  participant Runner as Codex Worker Runner
  participant Obj as Object Store Adapter
  participant Proof as Proof Ledger
  participant Approval as Approval Service
  participant GitHub as GitHub Adapter
  participant Memory as Memory Proposal Service

  Human->>Matrix: Submit task intent
  Matrix->>Gateway: Deliver untrusted task.created event
  Gateway->>Gateway: Authenticate, dedupe, validate JSON Schema
  Gateway->>API: Create runtime task command
  API->>Store: Persist task and source Matrix event reference
  API->>Router: Select capability for task node
  Router->>Policy: Check capability permissions
  Policy-->>Router: allow with policy version and reason
  Router-->>API: Selected repo.patch.codex version
  API->>WCM: Create Work Cell
  WCM->>Store: Persist worktree path, branch, base SHA, policy envelope
  WCM->>Runner: Launch Codex with cwd set to Work Cell worktree
  Runner->>Obj: Store stdout, stderr, JSONL, diff, validation logs
  Obj-->>Runner: Return artifact URIs and sha256 hashes
  Runner->>API: Submit structured result and artifact refs
  API->>Proof: Create proof entry
  Proof->>Store: Persist proof fields and verification status
  Proof->>Obj: Verify artifact refs and hashes
  Proof-->>API: Verified proof summary
  API->>Gateway: Project proof summary and artifact refs
  Gateway->>Matrix: Send proof summary, not raw proof logs
  API->>Policy: Check pr.create action
  Policy-->>API: approval_required
  API->>Approval: Request approval for pr.create and proof_id
  Approval->>Gateway: Project action-scoped approval request
  Gateway->>Matrix: Send approval request
  Human->>Matrix: Approve specific pr.create action
  Matrix->>Gateway: Deliver approval decision event
  Gateway->>API: Submit validated approval decision
  API->>Approval: Record decision for task_id, action, proof_id
  Approval-->>API: Approved exact action
  API->>GitHub: Create PR with approved proof reference
  GitHub-->>API: Return PR URL
  API->>Store: Persist PR artifact reference and task status
  API->>Memory: Propose memory update from verified proof
  Memory->>Store: Persist memory proposal, not live memory write
  API->>Gateway: Project completion and memory proposal summary
  Gateway->>Matrix: Send visible status projection
